        <item>
            <title>正式對任天堂法務部挑機   Switch 模擬器 Yuzu 稱已聘請律師回應盜版指控</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/03/04/yuzu-emulator-response-to-nintendo/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=yuzu-emulator-response-to-nintendo</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/03/04/yuzu-emulator-response-to-nintendo/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
